'''愛德·戴維爵士'''（Sir Ed Davey，{{bd|1965年|12月25日}}）是一位[[英國|英國]][[自由民主黨_(英國)|自由民主黨]]籍政治人物。

在1997年，他當選[[金斯頓和索比頓_(英國國會選區)|金斯頓和索比頓]]選區的下議院議員，並於2010年隨自民黨進入聯合政府，並於2012至2015年擔任能源和氣候變化大臣，但於2015年連任議員失敗並隨該黨下野。

戴維於[[2017年英國大選|2017年大選]]於金斯頓和索比頓選區再次當選為下議院議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14000770 |title=Kingston & Surbiton parliamentary constituency |work=BBC News |accessdate=2017-11-20 |archive-date=2017-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129032823/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14000770 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於2019年競選黨魁，但敗給[[喬·斯溫森|喬·斯溫森]]，隨後成為後者的副手。隨着[[2019年英國大選|同年大選]]斯溫森失去議席，他與黨主席布林頓一同代理黨魁職務，翌年正式當選黨魁。

2020年，他參與联名写信给[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]驻英大使[[刘晓明|刘晓明]]，谴责中国大陸政府[[新疆再教育营|针对新疆维吾尔穆斯林的行为]]。<ref>{{cite news |author1=法广 |title=英国近百名议员联名谴责中共针对新疆维吾尔穆斯林的行为 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200909-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%E8%81%94%E5%90%8D%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA |accessdate=2020-09-29 |agency=RFI |date=2020-09-10 |archive-date=2020-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910225118/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200909-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%E8%81%94%E5%90%8D%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=DAVID ALTON |title=Led by Siobhain McDonagh MP, 130 parliamentarians have today written to the Chinese Ambassador to the UK condemning treatment of Uyghur people in Xinjiang |url=https://davidalton.net/2020/09/08/led-by-siobhain-mcdonagh-mp-130-parliamentarians-have-today-written-to-the-chinese-ambassador-to-the-uk-condemning-treatment-of-uyghur-people-in-xinjiang/ |accessdate=2020-09-29 |date=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917001800/https://davidalton.net/2020/09/08/led-by-siobhain-mcdonagh-mp-130-parliamentarians-have-today-written-to-the-chinese-ambassador-to-the-uk-condemning-treatment-of-uyghur-people-in-xinjiang/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2021年，他又警示若英國因上述議題杯葛2022北京冬奧，北京當局可能就此進行報復式霸凌。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://amp.theguardian.com/world/2021/feb/15/libs-dems-warn-china-over-international-bullying-after-sanctions-threat-boycott-winter-olympics-uighurs |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-16 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227144734/https://amp.theguardian.com/world/2021/feb/15/libs-dems-warn-china-over-international-bullying-after-sanctions-threat-boycott-winter-olympics-uighurs |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他的父親是一位律師，母親則是一位教師<ref name="LibDem-EdwardDavey">{{cite web |url=http://www.libdems.org.uk/party/people/mr-edward-davey.html |title=Liberal Democrats: Edward Davey MP, Kingston & Surbiton |publisher=Liberal Democrats |accessdate=4 October 2006 |archive-date=2006-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060926070428/http://www.libdems.org.uk/party/people/mr-edward-davey.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

戴維會說[[英語|英語]]、[[法語|法語]]、[[德語|德語]]和[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.politics.co.uk/reference/edward-jonathon-davey|title=Edward Davey|website=politics.co.uk|access-date=2 May 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180503112517/http://www.politics.co.uk/reference/edward-jonathon-davey|archive-date=3 May 2018|url-status=dead}}</ref>。

2021年12月，戴維的[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]](COVID-19)檢測呈陽性<ref>{{cite news |title=Ed Davey: Lib Dem leader latest MP to self-isolate due to Covid |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-59654224 |access-date=15 December 2021 |work=BBC News |date=14 December 2021 |archive-date=2021-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218195115/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-59654224 }}</ref>。

